des:
This skill allows you to monitor your web application performance using New Relic API.
Before use this skill, open your Alexa app and click on the link to connect it with your Amazon account.

To use this skill you should:
- have a New Relic account;
- obtain an Application Id;
- obtain an API Key;
- configure your application using the link sent on your e-mail address.

This skill use New Relic API, but it's not developed by New Relic Inc.
